   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-heatmap-md",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 6.5 Correlation Heatmap — Numeric Features"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
